      "author_association" : "NONE",
      "body" : "FINALLY after 4 or 5 hours the message disappeared and I re-opened the GUI:\r\n![btc_back_on_track](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/16307383/36617398-47ee346a-18b5-11e8-8ca9-1271adc0063a.png)\r\n\r\nSo to everyone: WAIT for the window to close. If you close early and it screws it, run with **-reindex-chainstate** on the end. WAIT for it to reindex the data on the disk (it takes as long as it did to download/process) and then close/reopen and WAIT for it to continue loading the blockchain from it's last state.\r\n\r\nNow I have after several days of frustration I am damn near close to the full chain :)",
